com.xhive.dom.xlink.interfaces
Interface XhiveXLinkIf

All Known Subinterfaces:
XhiveArcIf, XhiveExtendedLinkIf, XhiveLocatorIf, XhiveResourceIf, XhiveSimpleLinkIf
public interface XhiveXLinkIf

Represents an XLink base type.

All link-types: simple, extended, arc, locator, resource, and title extend this interface.

(c) X-Hive Corporation B.V. (www.x-hive.com)
